title: BigFish - Enigma 7 - Match 3 - Requested [h33t][Wendy99]
description:
Enigma 7


Jane is a young archaeology student who`s gone 
missing. In the midst of a stormy downpour, 
you must embark on a journey to find her through 
an enigma of portals. A map inside an attic reveals 
a door containing fragments and Match 3 puzzle pieces. 
Highlight tiles under the artifacts to reveal clues. 
Can you match four or five tiles in a row and max out 
the power meter in Enigma 7?

    * Suspenseful Match 3 sequel
    * Captivating story
    * Solve puzzles and find Jane!

OS: Windows XP/Vista
CPU: 600 Mhz
RAM: 256 MB
DirectX: 7.0
Hard Drive: 64 MB
